result.name: Da Hong Pao hotpot

reviews.text:
Really popular hotpot venue, with a big selection of meats, seafood, dumplings, noodles and veg. All the usual areas are covered well. However I particularly like their deep fried fish skin, and the meat cuts were good quality.
There are two venues of this same restaurant on this street. They need the space as they are really popular. Also they open till REALLY late, so if you want to come for hotpot at 1Am they are still open until 02:30!
Good quality meat, hotpot soup base are rich in favour
😊😊lovely food and fresh
Poor reception; waiter don’t want to attend and don’t give explanation. Very bad place
One of the best in Hong Kong.  Constant quality.
